          %h3 Private Loans

          %p Many banks will also give loans to small businesses. The requirements for these loans may be more demanding and interest rates may also be higher. You are encouraged to contact your bank for current rates and terms.

          %p If you don’t have good credit, you may be able to use a “loan guarantee” program to apply for private bank loans with lower credit requirements but a slightly higher interest rate. California’s State Treasurer and Small Business Financial Development Corporation (SBFDC) both operate loan guarantee programs for small businesses.

          = render 'shared/link_box', link:'http://sbfdoc.com/programs/program-overview/', line_1:'VIEW', line_2:'SBFDC Loan Guarantee Program'

          = render 'shared/link_box', link:'http://www.treasurer.ca.gov/cpcfa/calcap/sb/summary.asp', line_1:'VIEW', line_2:'CalCAP'

